                                \t<damage/>\n\t\t\t</layout>\n                            </layoutDesc>\n                        </objectDesc>\n                        <handDesc>\n                            <handNote><p>Θ in a simple form, with a straight and attached cross-bar, squared lunate Σ and squared cursive Ω.</p><!--measurements from Korhonen-->\n                                <locus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Lines 1-2</locus>\n                                <dimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    <height unit=\"mm\">19-22</height>\n                                </dimensions>\n                                <locus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2</locus>\n                                <dimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    <height unit=\"mm\">not recorded</height>\n                                </dimensions>\n                            </handNote>\n                        </handDesc>\n                    </physDesc>\n                    <history>\n                        <origin>\n                            <origPlace>\n                                <placeName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462270\">Catina</placeName>\t\t\n                                <placeName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2525068\">Catania</placeName> \n                            \t<geo>37.49223, 15.07041</geo>\n\t\t</origPlace>\n                            <origDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0201\" notAfter-custom=\"0300\" precision=\"low\">3rd century CE</origDate>\n                        </origin>\n                        <provenance type=\"found\">Original discovery not recorded, but assumed to be from Catania (“visto che si tratta di un frammento poco notevole, con un’iscrizione greca su una faccia, e una latina sull’altra, sembra preferibile la provenienza locale” Korhonen 2004: 242).</provenance>\n                        <provenance type=\"observed\">Observed by Kaibel in Museo Biscari, later by Korhonen in magazzino superiore, Collezione Biscari.</provenance>\n                        <provenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None</provenance>\n                        <acquisition/>\n                    </history>\n                </msDesc>\n            </sourceDesc>\n        </fileDesc>\n        <encodingDesc>\n             <p>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines</p>\n             <xi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 <xi:fallback>\n                     <p>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values</p>\n                 </xi:fallback>\n             </xi:include>\n\t  <xi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     <xi:fallback>\n\t       <p>ISicily glyphs authority list</p>\n\t     </xi:fallback>\n\t   </xi:include>\n         </encodingDesc>\n        <profileDesc>\n            <calendarDesc>\n                <calendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    <p>Julian Calendar</p>\n                </calendar>\n            </calendarDesc>\n            <langUsage>\n                <language ident=\"en\">English</language>\n                <language ident=\"it\">Italian</language>\n                <language ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek</language>\n                <language ident=\"la\">Latin</language>\n                <language ident=\"he\">Hebrew</language>\n                <language ident=\"phn\">Phoenician</language>\n                <language ident=\"xpu\">Punic</language>\n                <language ident=\"osc\">Oscan</language>\n                <language ident=\"xly\">Elymian</language>\n                <language ident=\"scx\">Sikel</language>\n                <language ident=\"sxc\">Sikan</language>\n            </langUsage>\n            <textClass>\n                <keywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    <term ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary</term>\n                </keywords>\n            </textClass>\n        </profileDesc>\n        <revisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            <listChange>\n                <change when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database</change>\n                <change when=\"2019-07-11\" who=\"#AA\">Alex Antoniou Epidoc editing and English translation</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers</change>\n\t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n                <change when=\"2022-10-31\" who=\"#martaf\">Marta Fogagnolo revised the text encoding, added dimensions, translation and commentary</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001328_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001328.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n         </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/><w><expan><abbr>Θ</abbr><ex>εοῖς</ex></expan></w> <w><supplied reason=\"lost\"><expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>αταχθονίοις</ex></expan></supplied></w>\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/><persName type=\"attested\"><name>Σωτ<supplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">ηρ</supplied><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/></name></persName>\n                    <lb n=\"3\"/><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"line\"/>\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n                <listApp>\n                    <app><note>Text based on photographs</note></app>\n                    <app loc=\"line 2\"><note>Kaibel, Korhonen: Σωτ[ῆρ? ---]</note></app>\n                </listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <p>To the subterranean deities, Sot---</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <p>Agli dèi inferi, Sot---</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p>The invocation to the subterranean deities is followed by the name of the deceased, probably <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σωτῆρ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σώταιρος</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σώτειρα</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρία</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρίδας</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρίς</foreign> (attested in an inscription from Catania dated to the 3rd-5th cent. CE: IG 14.550 = <ref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001369\">ISic001369</ref>), <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Σωτήριχος</foreign> (attested in an inscription from Catania dated to the imperial age: CIL 10.7054 = <ref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000338\">ISic000338</ref>): on the names, see LGPN 3A: 417-419.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        <citedRange>\n                            <ref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">14.0507</ref>\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                        <citedRange>130</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl/>\n                </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\"><bibl/></listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
